[normal]humanitarian 
[normal]crises
[normal] in 
[normal]conflict zones
[normal],
[normal] 
[normal]such as 
[normal]in 
[normal]Palestine, Somalia, and Sri Lanka
[normal]. Such
[normal] a stance 
[normal]might even aggravate the situation by 
[normal]encourag
[normal]ing
[normal] less regulated and 
[normal]less cooperative
[normal] 
[normal]activities
[normal], even resulting in 
[normal]a strategic defeat
[normal].
[normal] 
